                        >
                            Salim Hussaini
                        </h1>
                        <p
                            class="tracking-tight lg:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-slate-200"
                        >
                            Fullstack Software Engineer
                        </p>

                        <p class="w-[75%]">
                            I build accessible, inclusive products and digital
